<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/709604-did-you-like-the-ending">Did you like the ending?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_709604'><a id="like_count_community_question_709604" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/709604?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F531262.A_Handful_of_Dust">like</a></span>

